{"word":"G1905 - ἐπερωτάω - eperōtáō - ep-er-o-tah'-o - Ask","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπερωτάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eperōtáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-er-o-tah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ask</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கேள், விசாரி, வினவு"},{"paragraph":"to accost one with an inquiry, put a question to, inquire of, ask, interrogate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G2065 - ἐρωτάω - erōtáō - er-o-tah'-o/2065\">G2065</a>; to <i>ask for</i>, that is, <i>inquire</i>, <i>seek:</i> - ask (after, questions), demand, desire, question.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1905/1905\">G1905</a>, <a href=\"#/G1906/1906\">G1906</a>, <a href=\"#/G2065/2065\">G2065</a>"}]}